data.description:
Welcome to your new home in the heart of a sought-after, family-friendly neighborhood! This charming split-level residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. As you step through the front door, you're greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere that extends throughout the home. The spacious living area provides ample room for relaxation and entertainment, boasting large windows that fill the space with natural light. The well-appointed kitchen is both functional and stylish. Upstairs, you'll find three nicely sized bedrooms, each offering a peaceful retreat at the end of the day. The master bedroom boasts its own en-suite bathroom for added privacy and convenience. Outside, the fenced-in backyard provides a safe and secure space for children and pets to play, while you enjoy a morning coffee or evening barbecue on the patio. One of the highlights of this community is the nearby swim club, offering the perfect opportunity to cool off on hot summer days and socialize with neighbors. Plus, with easy access to nearby restaurants and shopping, you'll never be far from everything you need.
Don't miss your chance to make this delightful home your own. Schedule a showing today and start picturing yourself living the good life in this wonderful neighborhood!
